HEADWORD: Toluric
<hw>To*lu"ric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Tol</ets>uic +
<ets>uric</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
